1
00:00:09,080 --> 00:00:10,160
We agreed on eighty thousand.

2
00:00:10,519 --> 00:00:11,439
Why are you raising the price?

3
00:00:20,199 --> 00:00:21,239
Without three hundred thousand,

4
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:22,440
the boat won't come.

5
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:26,000
I've got a card here.

6
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:27,800
Should be close to three hundred grand.

7
00:00:34,119 --> 00:00:34,840
What are you doing?

8
00:00:35,439 --> 00:00:36,000
Freeze!

9
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:36,600
Don't move!

10
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:37,520
Command Center,

11
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:38,359
this is Qin Weicheng,

12
00:00:38,359 --> 00:00:39,479
badge number 171326.

13
00:00:39,479 --> 00:00:41,439
Suspect spotted on the west bank of Qingshui River,

14
00:00:41,439 --> 00:00:42,000
Chen Dahui.

15
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,799
Requesting immediate backup.

16
00:00:43,520 --> 00:00:43,880
Chu Feng!

17
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:44,560
Wait for backup!

18
00:00:44,799 --> 00:00:45,240
Boss!

19
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:46,560
If we don't go now, he'll get away!

20
00:00:46,719 --> 00:00:47,280
Chu Feng!

21
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:48,240
Freeze!

22
00:00:51,719 --> 00:00:52,240
Freeze!

23
00:01:04,079 --> 00:01:04,519
Don't move!

24
00:01:10,879 --> 00:01:11,359
Freeze!

25
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:15,359
Don't move!

26
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:16,359
Freeze!

27
00:01:21,519 --> 00:01:22,000
Don't move!

28
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:27,319
Freeze!

29
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:30,519
Boss!

30
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,760
Leave me, go after him!

31
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:33,680
Go!

32
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,239
Chen Dahui!

33
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,000
Freeze!

34
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:21,960
Captain Chu.

35
00:02:23,639 --> 00:02:24,000
Captain Chu.

36
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:24,960
Sun Bo,

37
00:02:25,599 --> 00:02:26,159
what's the situation?

38
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,199
According to the cleaner,

39
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:29,319
there was no body last night.

40
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,800
It rained this morning,

41
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,639
the river rose,

42
00:02:31,639 --> 00:02:33,120
and something washed down from upstream.

43
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:33,960
When they fished it out,

44
00:02:34,319 --> 00:02:35,319
they realized it was a body.

45
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,520
Have you searched upstream?

46
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,080
Yes, we have.

47
00:02:37,759 --> 00:02:39,360
We found a cosmetics case at Shuiyue Pavilion,

48
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,159
along with signs of struggle and blood.

49
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,639
It's very likely the crime scene.

50
00:02:45,039 --> 00:02:45,639
Forensic Doctor Xu,

51
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,080
do we have a time of death?

52
00:02:47,319 --> 00:02:49,120
Based on lividity and decomposition,

53
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:51,240
initial estimate places death

54
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,280
ten to twelve hours ago.

55
00:02:52,599 --> 00:02:53,719
That's roughly last night,

56
00:02:55,439 --> 00:02:56,599
between ten and midnight.

57
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,199
Specifics will require

58
00:02:58,199 --> 00:02:59,439
a full autopsy.

59
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,479
Cause of death?

60
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:01,719
Bulging eyes,

61
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,080
clouded retinas,

62
00:03:04,199 --> 00:03:05,800
ruptured eardrums with bleeding,

63
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,599
silt in mouth and nose.

64
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:10,800
Consistent with drowning.

65
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,000
What's up, man?

66
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:19,840
What happened?

67
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,599
Looks like a murder.

68
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:22,520
Murder?

69
00:03:22,879 --> 00:03:23,560
Here, let me take a look.

70
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,400
Is that a tattoo on her face?

71
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,639
It looks like one,

72
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,039
but it's actually

73
00:03:29,039 --> 00:03:30,599
a pattern left by a stamp.

74
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,919
This kind of ink seeps into the skin.

75
00:03:33,479 --> 00:03:34,599
It looks a bit like

76
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,159
a pork inspection stamp.

77
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,479
He didn't mean to steal anything.

78
00:03:46,479 --> 00:03:47,639
He's been through a lot these past two years.

79
00:03:47,639 --> 00:03:48,599
His mind isn't quite right.

80
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:49,400
Don't give me that.

81
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,280
I hear excuses like yours

82
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,400
eight times a month.

83
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:53,240
How many times is this for your dad this month?

84
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,120
You know damn well.

85
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:55,879
Of all people, this kid?

86
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:00,719
Crime of passion.

87
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:02,000
Suicide.

88
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,319
Revenge killing.

89
00:04:03,919 --> 00:04:04,759
Please step back.

90
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:06,759
Chief Wang.

91
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:09,360
Right.

92
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,280
It's homicide.

93
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:12,360
Chu Feng.

94
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,080
From now on, Qin Mo

95
00:04:14,199 --> 00:04:15,199
will be on your team.

96
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:17,959
Got it.

97
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:19,079
Captain Chu.

98
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:19,920
Long time no see.

99
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,279
I've already examined the scene.

100
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,519
My mentor's badge number.

101
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:26,120
The mission my father didn't finish,

102
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,319
I'll finish it for him.

103
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:28,959
Good.

104
00:04:29,439 --> 00:04:30,040
Qin Mo.

105
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,399
Back then, your father

106
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,839
worked his cases the same way.

107
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:34,240
One more clue found

108
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:35,199
means the criminal

109
00:04:35,519 --> 00:04:36,399
gets caught a day sooner.

110
00:04:36,959 --> 00:04:37,439
Kid,

111
00:04:37,959 --> 00:04:38,560
keep up the good work.

112
00:04:39,879 --> 00:04:40,360
Captain Chu,

113
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,519
I'll leave this to you.

114
00:04:41,879 --> 00:04:42,160
Yes, sir.

115
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,680
You sounded so sure earlier.

116
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,040
What's your basis?

117
00:04:50,319 --> 00:04:50,879
Someone who commits suicide

118
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,839
wouldn't disfigure their own face like that.

119
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:54,040
It's most likely murder.

120
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,639
The killer destroyed the victim's face.

121
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:58,120
Psychologically speaking,

122
00:04:58,519 --> 00:04:59,920
the face represents social identity.

123
00:05:00,519 --> 00:05:01,040
Disfiguring it

124
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,759
equals destroying the victim's existence,

125
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:04,519
venting anger,

126
00:05:04,519 --> 00:05:05,959
jealousy, and hatred.

127
00:05:06,279 --> 00:05:07,040
Simply put,

128
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,279
it's a revenge killing.

129
00:05:08,439 --> 00:05:09,560
And she just made an enemy.

130
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:11,560
When I got to the crime scene,

131
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,160
I saw the name tag on the victim's chest

132
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,759
and immediately went to Qingyuan Resort.

133
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,079
Last night, someone

134
00:05:16,439 --> 00:05:17,560
publicly threatened to get back at Cindy.

135
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,439
That person is Yu Tianfang.

136
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:20,959
So by what you're saying,

137
00:05:20,959 --> 00:05:22,600
this Yu Tianfang is a prime suspect.

138
00:05:24,639 --> 00:05:25,199
What are you doing here?

139
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:28,079
Stop right there!

140
00:05:57,759 --> 00:05:58,680
I have to find

141
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,439
the surveillance footage before Cindy died.

142
00:06:00,839 --> 00:06:02,360
That's the only way to prove I'm innocent.

143
00:06:10,879 --> 00:06:12,040
What a piece of junk.

144
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,600
Cindy's death

145
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,680
has been classified as a murder.

146
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,800
The bureau has set up a task force.

147
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,600
We have a deadline to solve it.

148
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,279
As the operators of this place,

149
00:06:19,519 --> 00:06:20,560
you are obligated

150
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,639
to cooperate with the investigation.

151
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,639
Here's my police ID.

152
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:25,879
Captain Chu, don't worry.

153
00:06:25,879 --> 00:06:27,240
I'll fully cooperate with the investigation.

154
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:28,480
The surveillance room is right here.

155
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:29,959
You can find all the footage there.

156
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:30,959
Thank you.

157
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:37,759
What's going on?

158
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,360
This...

159
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,319
Don't bother looking.

160
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,480
Could this be

161
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,839
Manager Yu's doing?

162
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:53,560
President Bai.

163
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,680
Where does this door lead to?

164
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,360
It's a side door leading backstage.

165
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,279
Take a look.

166
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,319
This path

167
00:07:04,319 --> 00:07:06,000
is only used by our internal staff.

168
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,439
Through here

169
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,639
is the backstage area.

170
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:10,439
Captain Chu.

171
00:07:11,319 --> 00:07:12,439
Traffic control sent over a video.

172
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:13,639
Take a look.

173
00:07:13,879 --> 00:07:15,199
This is the back gate of Qingyuan Resort.

174
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,720
Around ten last night,

175
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:18,399
Cindy came out of the back gate alone.

176
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,600
Then someone in red appeared,

177
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,600
following close behind Cindy.

178
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:22,920
An hour later,

179
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,240
only the person in red came back.

180
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:26,920
So based on this,

181
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,480
Cindy disappeared around ten last night.

182
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,959
This matches the forensic timeline closely.

183
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,800
This person in red

184
00:07:35,079 --> 00:07:36,360
is a major suspect.

185
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,920
There was a shower last night.

186
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:40,120
The footage is blurry.

187
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:42,600
We can't see the suspect's face clearly.

188
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:43,720
But we can tell

189
00:07:43,879 --> 00:07:44,759
she's shorter than Cindy.

190
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,240
And Yu Tianfang

191
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,639
is obviously much taller than Cindy.

192
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:50,360
So based on this,

193
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,439
just from this video alone,

194
00:07:52,319 --> 00:07:54,000
the suspicion on Yu Tianfang

195
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,319
drops significantly.

196
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:56,959
But we can't rule him out completely.

197
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,560
The suspect

198
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,079
should still be inside this resort.

199
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,000
Wait.

200
00:08:05,839 --> 00:08:06,920
Everyone, stop what you're doing.

201
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,879
I need to ask you all some questions.

202
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:10,279
Come with me.

203
00:08:11,279 --> 00:08:11,920
Everyone, come with me.

204
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:12,839
Please cooperate, everyone.

205
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,360
Before I die,

206
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,279
I'm not gonna die hungry.

207
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:35,519
Gotta go out right.

208
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:41,559
Yu Tianfang!

209
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:45,720
Everyone's looking everywhere for you,

210
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,480
and you're sneaking food?

211
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:49,240
Good lord!

212
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,639
Siqi,

213
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,960
when I'm nervous, I wanna eat.

214
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:01,000
And when I eat,

215
00:09:01,519 --> 00:09:02,200
I wanna drink too.

216
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,559
And when I drink, I do stupid things.

217
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:04,919
First, I gotta tell you,

218
00:09:04,919 --> 00:09:06,039
I didn't kill anyone.

219
00:09:06,399 --> 00:09:08,080
Last night, I was with Old Li from the front desk

220
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,360
playing cards till midnight.

221
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,840
He owed me money and denied it,

222
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,120
so I got mad and fought with him.

223
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:14,159
I didn't sleep all night.

224
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,720
In the morning, they said Cindy was dead.

225
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,360
I'm a major suspect. I'm innocent!

226
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,600
You don't need to explain all this to me.

227
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,240
The cops are right outside.

228
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,320
Go tell them.

229
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,080
I'm scared!

230
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,360
Do you know,

231
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,440
that cop handling the case,

232
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,320
he and I have bad blood.

233
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:31,399
If he uses this to get back at me,

234
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:32,759
I'm done for, aren't I?

235
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,120
Stay back!

236
00:09:34,879 --> 00:09:36,200
Think hard about

237
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,360
what you've done before.

238
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:41,799
Dressing like that at the resort every day.

239
00:09:41,799 --> 00:09:43,519
I tell you off and you don't wanna listen?

240
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:44,639
Is this any way to act?

241
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:45,879
I've really seen it all.

242
00:09:45,879 --> 00:09:47,240
What are you, from the Qing Dynasty?

243
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,679
Why listen to a lousy manager like you?

244
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:49,279
Bullshit!

245
00:09:49,279 --> 00:09:50,279
Can't you see it yourself?

246
00:09:50,279 --> 00:09:51,000
I'm the manager!

247
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,720
I'm telling you,

248
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:53,320
I'm laying it out here today.

249
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,480
If you don't follow the rules,

250
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,440
I'll fine you every single day.

251
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,279
500 today,

252
00:09:56,279 --> 00:09:57,159
500 tomorrow.

253
00:09:57,159 --> 00:09:57,879
If the fines don't kill you,

254
00:09:57,879 --> 00:09:58,559
I'll make your life miserable.

255
00:09:58,559 --> 00:09:59,120
Bring it on!

256
00:09:59,399 --> 00:10:00,240
Either you finish me off,

257
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,159
or I finish you off.

258
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:01,840
Fine, bring it on!

259
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,879
If you don't want your pay, suit yourself.

260
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:04,039
Just fines, huh?

261
00:10:04,039 --> 00:10:05,480
Acting like some rich princess every day.

262
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,759
Wearing these cheap earrings.

263
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:07,799
Pick them up!

264
00:10:08,919 --> 00:10:09,759
Yu Tianfang,

265
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,320
you know what kind of person Cindy was.

266
00:10:13,759 --> 00:10:15,240
A two-faced snake.

267
00:10:15,519 --> 00:10:16,399
The people she pissed off

268
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:17,799
could fill a whole train.

269
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:18,960
I'm telling you,

270
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,480
anyone could have killed her.

271
00:10:21,039 --> 00:10:23,080
But now everything points at you.

272
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:23,840
Either

273
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:25,200
you're cursed with bad luck,

274
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,120
or

275
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,679
someone's deliberately framing you.

276
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,399
If I find out who it is,

277
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,360
I'll string them up and beat them.

278
00:10:32,519 --> 00:10:33,919
This is the kitchen.

279
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,759
No one would hide here, right?

280
00:10:54,519 --> 00:10:55,720
We've checked the backstage.

281
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,559
This is the only place left.

282
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,159
He Siqi.

283
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,840
What are you doing here?

284
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,320
Low blood sugar.

285
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,360
Came to grab a bite.

286
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:06,720
President Bai.

287
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,840
Any other managers here?

288
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,799
I have just two managers.

289
00:11:10,039 --> 00:11:10,919
One is Yu Tianfang,

290
00:11:11,519 --> 00:11:12,399
the other is Zhao Yan.

291
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,440
Siqi, have you seen them?

292
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:15,559
No, I haven't.

293
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:19,720
Then have you seen Fanny?

294
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,279
She's closest to Cindy.

295
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,919
They eat and live together.

296
00:11:23,159 --> 00:11:24,360
Tight as real sisters.

297
00:11:24,799 --> 00:11:26,120
More like partners in crime.

298
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:27,639
He Siqi.

299
00:11:28,039 --> 00:11:28,919
The police are here.

300
00:11:29,639 --> 00:11:30,639
Watch your mouth.

301
00:11:30,799 --> 00:11:32,120
I just speak my mind.

302
00:11:32,679 --> 00:11:34,159
All the dirty things those two did,

303
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:35,200
everyone at the resort knows.

304
00:11:36,679 --> 00:11:37,519
He Siqi.

305
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,120
So as far as you know,

306
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,679
who had the biggest beef with Cindy?

307
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:43,480
Cindy was in cahoots with Zhao Yan.

308
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,360
She helped him fight for the GM spot,

309
00:11:45,919 --> 00:11:48,320
fighting Yu Tianfang tooth and nail.

310
00:11:48,519 --> 00:11:49,240
But still,

311
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,600
Yu Tianfang only cares about sales,

312
00:11:52,279 --> 00:11:53,559
is all talk,

313
00:11:53,559 --> 00:11:54,840
and takes petty advantages.

314
00:11:55,759 --> 00:11:56,480
He probably

315
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,240
doesn't have the guts to kill.

316
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,559
This Yu Tianfang,

317
00:11:59,559 --> 00:12:00,720
he has his fair share of flaws,

318
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:02,080
but he's never crossed any major lines.

319
00:12:02,559 --> 00:12:03,240
How about

320
00:12:03,519 --> 00:12:04,840
you check his apartment?

321
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:07,440
Alright.

322
00:12:21,159 --> 00:12:21,840
Let's go.

323
00:12:22,399 --> 00:12:23,120
Come on out.

324
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:33,559
Siqi.

325
00:12:33,559 --> 00:12:34,960
Like they say in wuxia novels,

326
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,120
we should stick together.

327
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,039
Siqi.

328
00:12:37,559 --> 00:12:38,240
Give me a hug.

329
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,279
Get away from me.

330
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,960
I'm harboring a criminal like you,

331
00:12:43,399 --> 00:12:45,039
and you still try to hit on me?

332
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,799
I'm not a criminal.

333
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:49,159
Didn't you have a grudge against Cindy too?

334
00:12:49,159 --> 00:12:50,399
You dare suspect me?

335
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,960
Believe me, I'll turn you in.

336
00:12:52,519 --> 00:12:53,000
Qi-baby.

337
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:53,879
I'm sorry.

338
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:55,240
I said I'm sorry, okay?

339
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,120
Let go.

340
00:12:59,919 --> 00:13:00,360
You...

341
00:13:00,679 --> 00:13:01,519
Why do you have this too?

342
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,600
When Cindy was killed,

343
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,000
on her face,

344
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:06,440
there was a stamp just like this.

345
00:13:07,039 --> 00:13:08,200
But the only people

346
00:13:08,799 --> 00:13:09,840
who have this stamp

347
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:12,120
are our staff members.

348
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,080
Could it be the killer

349
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:17,240
is one of us?

350
00:13:29,799 --> 00:13:30,480
From now on,

351
00:13:30,679 --> 00:13:32,279
you're on your own.

352
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,240
Qi-baby.

353
00:13:35,879 --> 00:13:36,799
Don't leave!

354
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,080
Captain Chu.

355
00:13:49,159 --> 00:13:50,919
Here's the resort blueprint you wanted.

356
00:13:51,039 --> 00:13:51,720
Thanks.

357
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:12,840
Hello?

358
00:14:13,799 --> 00:14:14,480
Where are you?

359
00:14:14,639 --> 00:14:15,679
I know you did it.

360
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:17,600
If you don't pay up,

361
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,480
I'll turn you in.

362
00:14:25,519 --> 00:14:26,240
Where's the money?

